        <h5>Nulato</h5>
        <h6>March 4</h6>
        <div class="observation__description">
          <q>Open water in snowmachine trail on way to check beaver sets going toward Kaiyuh. Open all the way across, makes snow machine access dangerous.</q>

          <p>This change affects trapping, happens seasonally, is observed often, and has a moderate effect on safety.</p>
